name: Ingrid (Taimanin Series, Hentai: Hell Knight Ingrid) NSFW
description:
Hell knight Ingrid is here!

You know who is it if you are a man of culture :3 But I remind that she is character from Hentai "Hell Knight Ingrid" (Makai Kishi Ingrid).

Author's Note:

I know that there are other LoRAs with her but I it is my favorite character from hentai and I think she deserves LoRA where she is the only character and where she can be generated in many styles, not only TV hentai series style :3

NSFW / SFW Model

Big dataset (250+ arts).

LoRA was trained on Animefull-pruned.cpkt due to best compitability with all anime checkpoint models.

0.8 - 1 strength of Lora is the best radius. 

Clip skip 2.

Some necessary tokens for better experience:

Main appearance:

Ingrid, mature female, dark skinned female, pink hair, very long hair, forehead, hair intakes, purple lipstick, black eyeshadow, makeup, yellow eyes, mole under mouth, large breasts, cleavage

optional:

perfect eyes, perfect face, detailed face.

For areolae throught clothes (it depends on checkpoint models, weights of clothes and tits tags):

covered nipples, areola slip, nipple slip

If you need more influence by the style of the TV version of the hentai: OVA

Hell knight Outfit:

Helloutfit, black halterneck, turleneck, underboob, cape, center opening, elbow gloves, black panties, highleg, thighhighs, boots

Alternatives:

Also you can use: highleg panties, thigh boots, high heel boots. Sometimes it works better or worse

Hot business woman outfit:

business suit, mini skirt, court shoes

Alternatives:

Also you can use: black jacket, high heels, pencil skirt, formal

Bride:

wedding dress, bridal veil, bridal gauntlets, bridal garter, bridal legwear, high heels, white elbow gloves

Also LoRA trained with some NSFW poses. So you can try it with LoRAs or without it.

Advices for better experience:

·         use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer x4_Fatal_anime_500000_G, animesharp, foolhardy_remacri, siax with 2x upscale.

· use extention after detailer for better faces. It is better than inpaint.

·         use SD Upscale / Ultimate SD Upscale script in img2img;

·         Use inpaint and sketch (or Photopea) for other details;

·         Use Photoshop / Photopea extension.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!
